{/* Guided Meditation Section */}

Guided Meditation

Breathing Exercises

  • Pranayama (4-7-8 Breathing)

    1. Inhale quietly through the nose for 4 counts
    2. Hold the breath for 7 counts
    3. Exhale completely through mouth for 8 counts
    4. Repeat the cycle 4 times

  • Box Breathing

    1. Inhale for 4 counts
    2. Hold for 4 counts
    3. Exhale for 4 counts
    4. Hold for 4 counts
    5. Repeat the cycle

Meditation Techniques

  • Mindfulness Meditation

    Focus on your breath and observe your thoughts without judgment.

  • Body Scan Meditation

    Progressively focus attention on different parts of your body.

{/* Nutritional Tips Section */}

Nutritional Tips for Mental Well-being

Foods for Emotional Balance

  • Complex carbohydrates (whole grains, vegetables)
  • Omega-3 rich foods (flaxseeds, walnuts)
  • Protein-rich foods (lentils, chickpeas)
  • Probiotic foods (yogurt, fermented foods)

Ayurvedic Recommendations

  • Warm milk with turmeric before bedtime
  • Fresh fruits and vegetables
  • Nuts and seeds for brain health
  • Herbs like Brahmi and Ashwagandha
